  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present study is to evaluate effects of a clinical pharmacist service on
      health-related quality of life and prescribing of drugs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A randomized controlled trial is performed in two internal medicine wards at Sahlgrenska
      University Hospital, Göteborg, Sweden.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
